            <div class="course-cert-faq-summary">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-70">
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lean-six-sigma-yellow-belt-training-1">
                            <h3>Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Training</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-1">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-1">1. What is Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt training is a program that gives you knowledge of all the Six Sigma tools and techniques under the Yellow Belt level, as per the International Association for Six Sigma Certification (IASSC).&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-2">2. How long will it take for me to complete the LSSYB Curriculum?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The LSSYB curriculum is quite detailed, as it covers all the fundamental topics, concepts, and tools of Lean Six Sigma. You will also learn how to assist project teams with your skills. So, it may take you a few months to completely understand the curriculum.&nbsp;</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-3">3. Why should I choose KnowledgeHut for LSSYB over other courses?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You should choose KnowledgeHut for LSSYB due to several reasons. Our course curriculum has been designed in a phased manner to help you grasp concepts better, from world-class trainers. You will also be mentored by industry experts and given several resources to help you learn.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-4">4. What practical skills can I expect to have after completing this course? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The <b>Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Certification</b> helps you achieve the following practical skills: </p>
