                                            <p>With the Six Sigma Yellow Belt certification, you can enjoy a rewarding and lucrative career as a quality management and control professional.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-3">3. Does Six Sigma Yellow Belt help get job?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, of course it does. With the certification, you can accelerate your career in Quality Management or even better your skills by pursuing the Green Belt certification.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-4">4. What is the use of Six Sigma Yellow belt certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You can use your certification as a stepping stone to access better career opportunities in Quality Control and Management.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-5">5. What are the benefits of the Six Sigma Yellow Belt Certification? </a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The intense competition in the markets require organizations to ensure that their processes are optimized and there is maximum gain with minimum wastage. Six Sigma refers to a system where business problems that aren’t giving the desired outcomes are identified, and practices are put in place for their requirements. Six Sigma Yellow Belts are important members of the Six Sigma team as they assist in monitoring and evaluating work progress and process enhancements. The Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Certification is a reflection of the holder’s grasp of the Six Sigma concepts and ability to apply the same for organizational benefit.<br></p>
