                "text": "<p>The LSSYB curriculum is quite detailed, as it covers all the fundamental topics, concepts, and tools of Lean Six Sigma. You will also learn how to assist project teams with your skills. So, it may take you a few months to completely understand the curriculum.&nbsp;</p>"
            }
