                "text": "<p>Lean Six Sigma certifications are offered by the IASSC in partnership with PEOPLECERT. </p><p>This is the first level of the Lean Six Sigma Certification scheme, and more advanced levels include the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification, and the Lean Six Sigma Black Belt Certification.&nbsp;</p>"
