        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How to get Six Sigma Yellow Belt certification? ",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You can get the Six Sigma Yellow Belt Certification using the following steps: </p><p><b>Step 1: Get Trained  </b></p><p>Enrol for an upcoming training program by KnowledgeHut an accredited training organization (ATO) with PeopleCert® and attend the 8-hour intensive training.    </p><p><b>Step 2: Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Exam™ Exam  </b></p><p>Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Exam™ exam and score a minimum of 70% in this 120-minute multiple choice exam.    </p><p><b>Step 3: Get Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt Certified &nbsp;</b></p><p>Download the e-certificate. You are now a Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt certified professional. &nbsp;</p>"
